{"tid":487871,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[文科撚入]想問有無形容反對派扮支持者搞事嘅成語？","createTime":"2017-12-03T07:21:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T11:43:45.000Z","uid":55552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5e1c596afdd54a0a52b801710a1408c8de744be9","tid":487871,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T07:21:19.000Z","msg":"即係假設一場選舉，有候選人A同候選人B，而候選人A嘅支持者，去刻意假扮成候選人B嘅支持者，再去以候選人B支持者嘅身份去講啲弱智言論同埋不停撩事鬥非，嚟導致其他人對候選人B印象變差。<br />\n<br />\n有無一個四字成語可以形容呢種人，或者呢種行為？"},{"pid":"4976efb0412ef83da0ad35a7e1977d939de977bf","tid":487871,"uid":36441,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T07:47:31.000Z","msg":"鬼"},{"pid":"ff13610d470594470e099d8ed50ef3d0ae370fd1","tid":487871,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T09:31:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鬼</blockquote><br />\n我要四字成語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e2e71bdd6699dd6edf7e416dac76b86e7d1323b","tid":487871,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T15:14:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b5efa2abc9c1ea6349ed1dbd2d6314a48fd1a0","tid":487871,"uid":138552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T15:33:11.000Z","msg":"嫁禍於人"},{"pid":"1d233c713e0827b45c1e3cd90d60de9cd04a24af","tid":487871,"uid":156394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T15:39:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鬼</blockquote><br />\n鬼到唔鬼"},{"pid":"40025b9ef9e9de6981cc8a52365354750096fb49","tid":487871,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T21:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9aea86530acb8f7c85bbb4e584bfdba74db4b25","tid":487871,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T21:59:06.000Z","msg":"禍水東引?<br />\n栽贓嫁禍？"},{"pid":"603078dae5a2bc190944658